_sText:
This map was a VERY random map we were bored one day and decided we wanted to make a randomly fun but dare i say "odd" map. This is the product of to little sleep and brains going of coke for fuel. Hope you enjoy. 

-*- IF YOU USE THE MAP IN A SERVER PLZ LET US KNOW we would like to see it in play-*-

 THIS IS A BETA we want to see what you and others think of it so plzzz help us out and get this map out there.

Story:
This is a more future based era where computers rule. The T's are trying there best to take the SUPER COMPUTER lab over for their own use. 

T: Beat the CT's down even if it means slapping them to death!!!

CT: Stop T's from slapping you to death!!!

Map features:
Random spinning objects (makes game play a bit more fair)
Cool map texture for the future (we hope)
LOADS of little puzzles (walk through walls and hidden holes)
Chaotic yet somehow fun gameplay
Hidden teles (visible from certain spots)
AND A GIANT SPINNING CUBE IN THE MIDDLE!!!

File size: 2.27mb (rar file)

Well we hope you have fun PLEASE pleave feed back since this is a beta so we can give you what you want :) REMEBER please let us now how this map does if its on yours or someone elses server and if you can give us IP adress THANK YOU!!

-Xombine Studios
